cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY. 

The paper proposes a learning from demonstration approach for task decomposition and control, which involves machine learning, robotics, and computer vision. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.RO (Robotics), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also uses image-based observations, which suggests that it may fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper deals with control, which could place it under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
